text: Jack The Ripper Lover / No End is the debut single of Swedish rock band Brainbombs. It was self-released on vinyl and around 533 copies were made. The person on the album cover is English serial killer Peter Sutcliffe. == Track listing == == References == Category:Rock albums Category:1989 albums Category:Brainbombs songs
title: Jack The Ripper Lover / No End (Brainbombs single)
